column4: Isn't it, isn't it! We'll soon have a little baby in our family, to raise and dote upon as much as we want!
And I'll soon have a girlfriend with a giant bloated belly, mmm, just the thought is arousing.
P-Please don't say embarrassing stuff like that. Although… I wouldn't mind having sex like that either.
Hahaha. I can't wait for the day.
